# DMS V2 — Implementation Walkthrough

## Summary

Upgraded the Document Management System from V1 (basic file upload/review) to V2 with **dynamic form builder**, **dedicated teacher APIs/UI**, **bulk ZIP downloads**, and **secure temporary download links**.

---

## Changes Made

### Schema Upgrades (Phase 1)

| File | Changes |
|------|---------|
| [DocumentRequirement.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/DocumentRequirement.ts) | Added `custom_fields[]` (7 field types), `requires_file_upload` flag |
| [DocumentSubmission.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/DocumentSubmission.ts) | Added `form_responses` Map, `additional_files[]`, made file fields optional |
| [AuditLog.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/AuditLog.ts) | Added `APPROVE`, `REJECT`, `UPLOAD`, `BULK_DOWNLOAD` actions |

### Teacher APIs (Phase 2) — 7 Routes

| Route | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| [GET requirements](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/requirements/route.ts) | List scoped to teacher's assigned subjects |
| [POST requirements](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/requirements/route.ts) | Create assignment-type with custom fields |
| [GET/PUT/DELETE requirements/id](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/requirements/%5Bid%5D/route.ts) | Manage own requirements + submission stats |
| [GET submissions](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/submissions/route.ts) | Paginated, filtered by status/requirement |
| [PUT submissions/id/review](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/submissions/%5Bid%5D/review/route.ts) | Approve/reject with history archiving |
| [GET submissions/id/download](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/submissions/%5Bid%5D/download/route.ts) | Secure Cloudinary signed URL (15min) |

### Bulk Download (Phase 3)

| Route | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| [Admin bulk download](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/bulk-download/route.ts) | ZIP all submissions per requirement (max 200) |
| [Teacher bulk download](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/documents/submissions/bulk-download/route.ts) | Same but scoped to teacher's requirements |

### Student API Updates (Phase 4)

- [Upload route](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/upload/route.ts): Handles `form_responses`, validates required custom fields, uploads additional files
- [List route](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/route.ts): Returns `custom_fields` for dynamic rendering

### Admin API Updates

- [Admin requirements route](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/requirements/route.ts): Accepts `custom_fields` + `requires_file_upload`
- [Admin requirements/id route](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/requirements/%5Bid%5D/route.ts): Update supports custom fields

### UI Changes

| Page | Key Features |
|------|-------------|
| [Teacher documents](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(teacher)/teacher/documents/page.tsx) | Two-tab UI, form builder (7 types), bulk download, review modal with form responses |
| [Teacher sidebar](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/teacher/TeacherSidebar.tsx) | Added "Assignments" nav link |
| [Admin documents](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/documents/page.tsx) | Form builder, bulk download button, `requires_file_upload` toggle, form responses in review |
| [Student documents](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(student)/student/documents/page.tsx) | Dynamic form renderer, additional file uploads, client-side validation |

---

## Verification

- **TypeScript build**: `npx tsc --noEmit` — **0 errors**, exit code 0
- **Dependencies**: `archiver` + `@types/archiver` installed

## Custom Field Types Supported

`text` · `textarea` · `number` · [date](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/documents/page.tsx#209-212) · `dropdown` · `checkbox` · `file`

Each field supports: label, required flag, placeholder, options (dropdown), file type/size limits (file type)
